file,prometheus-praxis.rights-gate.v1.aln
shard,PrometheusPraxisRightsGate
description,Unified rights-gate over sleep-corridors, Vt, ecosafety, RoH/LIFEFORCE, blast radius, and sensor trust, with Allow/Derate/Stop bindings to Kani-verified Rust governance functions in the Organichain / Reality.os governance crate

