ROW,meta,scalar,serde_json_version,1.0.120,string,immutable,Serde JSON version
ROW,meta,flag,forwardOnlyEvolution,true,bool,nonwaivable,Upgrades must be forward-only and non-reversible; no downgrades or rollbacks at any layer
ROW,meta,flag,noSimulatedSystems,true,bool,nonwaivable,All integrations must target biophysical reality; no simulated or toy safety that disables protections

