ROW,epoch,scalar,corridor_depth,0.0,float,range0,1,Aggregated N2N3 depth or safety-corridor index from sleep and state shards
ROW,epoch,scalar,corridor_uncertainty,0.0,float,range0,1,Combined uncertainty Ucomb from staging and sensor models
