ROW,rights,scalar,policyId,prometheus-neurorights-core,string,primarykey,Neurorights baseline for this gate
ROW,rights,flag,mentalPrivacy,true,bool,nonwaivable,No raw dream content, inner speech, or soul constructs exported
ROW,rights,flag,cognitiveLiberty,true,bool,nonwaivable,Participation and BCI loops must remain voluntary; refusal never penalized
ROW,rights,flag,mentalIntegrity,true,bool,nonwaivable,No harmful modulation of mental state, no forced arousal or distress
